    "id": "speaker-30",
    "name": "Arkayla Tenney-Howard",
    "role": "Owner, Creator",
    "organization": "Wildflower Communications",
    "bio": "Arkayla Tenney-Howard is a writer, marketing consultant and workshop facilitator based in the St. Louis area. Her background is in public relations and she uses strategic storytelling to support local nonprofit organizations and small businesses. Her love of writing fuels her teaching a variety of workshops including Canva classes, Journaling courses and more.",
    "presentationExperience": "Canva for Fundraising, St. Louis Community Foundation \nVisioning For Entrepreneurs, Baddies With Business Entrepreneurial Collective \nThe Power of Journaling, monthly sessions with Damned Good People Coffee Co + Nonprofit",
